data.title: Reenst Lesemann
data.text: Prior to his association with Tall Oaks Capital, Reenst ran a series of successful businesses including a maritime logistics spin off, TradeSource, Inc., that he created, led and managed. During his career, he has been responsible for all aspects of business management including strategic planning, marketing, and information services. Mr. Lesemann's customers ranged from Fortune 50 to small businesses and were located in over 20 countries. He most recently served as Chief Executive Officer for D&R Development in Charlottesville, Virginia. Prior to joining D&R Development, he held various positions at Atlantic Services Group, Inc. and its affiliates in Charleston, South Carolina, including Vice President Operations, and President and Chief Executive Officer for four of Atlantic's logistics subsidiaries.
